Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:29.96,tanda-5,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\bord3\shad0\c&HCC920E&\pos(960,75)\3c&HFFFFFF&}(Tensura) Bereinkarnasi Malah Menjadi Slime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:44.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kalian...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:47.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian meremehkanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:50.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:59.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian mengajukan ini dengan sadar\Nbahwa aku Raja Iblis, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:02.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Surat tuntutan yang merendahkan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:07.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuntutan yang diajukan Dewan\Nbenar-benar keterlaluan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:14.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, membangun jalur kereta sihir\Nhingga Kerajaan Ingrassia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:19.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seluruh biaya konstruksi dan pengeluarannya\Nditanggung oleh Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:23.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kedua, menyediakan senjata\Ndan perlengkapan berkualitas tinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:26.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pihak Tempest diminta bekerja sama
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:29.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}demi memperkuat militer\NNegara-Negara Barat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:35.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketiga, dungeon yang muncul di Tempest\Nadalah harta milik umat manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:39.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, Dewan turut dilibatkan\Ndalam pengelolaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:43.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keempat, sebagai syarat bergabung dengan Dewan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:46.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sejumlah iuran wajib dibayarkan tiap tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:51.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, mengenai pemilihan anggota dewan,\Ndemi alasan keamanan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hanya manusia yang diperbolehkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:03:00.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sama saja dengan mengatakan bahwa\Nnegeriku ingin dijadikan budak, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:05.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya-Yang Mulia Rimuru,\Nkami tidak bermaksud begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:10.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, kami hanya ingin bisa lebih dekat\Ndengan negara Anda, jadi kelepasan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:14.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya kelepasan\Nmemandang rendah negara kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:22.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebablasan! Bodohnya aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:25.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hubungan yang telah kubangun\Ndengan manusia bisa terancam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:26.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lapor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:32.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terdeteksi pengaruh Gangguan Spiritual\Nyang mengendalikan area ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:34.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gangguan Spiritual?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:43.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada yang mencoba mengendalikan jalannya\Nsidang ini lewat para anggota dewan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:47.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, tetapi gelombang amarah Master
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:50.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}telah menciptakan celah pada skill tersebut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:52.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ingin melepas Gangguan Spiritual?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:57.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:03:59.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:04.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajar Yang Mulia Rimuru marah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:08.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Be-Benar, siapa yang mengajukan\Ntuntutan seenaknya begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:09.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Betul itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:13.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, syarat-syarat itu sama sekali\Ntidak dibahas sebelumnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:17.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya para anggota dewan itu\Nsudah sadar kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:20.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan, ini Dominasi Spiritual?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:23.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, rasanya tidak sekuat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:26.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya Gangguan Spiritual\Nyang mempersempit sudut pandang mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ulah siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:32.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya bukan Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:36.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak akan menggunakan metode\Nyang meninggalkan bukti begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:41.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti pelakunya mereka\Nyang terlihat santai di sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:47.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelihatannya masih punya rencana\Nmeski sudah membuat Raja Iblis marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:52.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada pasukan bersenjata sedang mendekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:57.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:00.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa ini?\NSidangnya masih berlanjut!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:05.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi-lagi ada yang datang bergerombol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada beberapa yang mukanya familier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:16.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran Elric, siapa mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:19.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya yang memanggil mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:22.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk memberi pelajaran pada berandal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:25.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Gaban, Anda sudah gila?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:26.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perbuatan Kerajaan Ingrassia, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:32.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Gaban,\Nkami tidak diberi tahu rencana ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:34.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:39.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya semua yang ada di sini\Ntakut dengan Raja Iblis Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:41.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Faktanya seperti itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:45.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, saya akan mengalahkan\Ndan menundukkan Raja Iblis Rimuru di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:47.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau berhasil,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:51.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oktagram dan Veldora pun\Nakan menjadi pion kami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:55.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan berarti bisa seenaknya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:59.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia Rimuru,\Nada kesalahpahaman di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan kehendak semua anggota dewan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:05.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran, apa maksud dari perbuatan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:10.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hinata, aku kecewa padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:13.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelindung umat manusia\Ntakut pada Raja Iblis
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:15.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan malah meninggalkan perannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:17.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa katamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:22.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seandainya kamu mau bekerja sama,\Naku akan memperlakukanmu dengan hormat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kuperkenalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:27.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Gaiye, tentara bayaran kelas satu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:31.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}beserta ketua dan anggota grup\Ntentara bayaran ternama "Vert".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:36.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ternyata dia bosnya Tim Amukan Hijau.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:42.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemudian, dialah pria terkuat di Ingrassia\Nsekaligus kesatriaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:46.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Komandan Kesatria Kerajaan Ingrassia, Reiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:51.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengumpulkan yang terbaik\Ndemi menumpas Raja Iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:56.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terlalu percaya diri bahwa\Nhanya dirimu yang kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:59.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu cukup menonton\Npenumpasan Raja Iblis ini dari sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:04.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan membawa masalah bagi\NGereja Suci Barat, apalagi Ruberios...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:06.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:10.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya di sini sebagai saksi pihak ketiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:13.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya tidak bisa membiarkan tindakan\Ngegabah seorang individu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:16.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kecuali ini keputusan resmi Dewan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:20.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya Komandan Kesatria Suci,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:25.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi mengalahkan raja iblis lemah saja tidak bisa,\Nmalah saling menjilat satu sama lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:30.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya kalian kabur\Nsambil mengompol, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:37.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para anggota dewan!\NTunjukkan tekad kalian sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:42.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadilah pahlawan yang menumpas Raja Iblis,\Natau jadilah musuh umat manusia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:46.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku, Elric von Ingrassia,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:50.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}percaya bahwa kalian semua\Nakan membuat pilihan yang benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:56.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau melakukan pemungutan suara\Nsetelah sejauh ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:08:00.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah jelas, bukan?\NIni adalah Dewan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:05.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan tidak perlu ada pemungutan suara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:07.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita ambil keputusan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:10.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalahkan dan tundukkan Raja Iblis di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang setuju, berdirilah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:17.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon renungkan kembali\Nkata-kata Tuan Gaban.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Percaya diri sekali dia.\NKalau kita berhasil mengalahkan\NRaja Iblis Rimuru di sini...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:23.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan...\NKalau kita berhasil mengalahkan\NRaja Iblis Rimuru di sini...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:24.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:28.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketika individu Souei menyelidiki\Nkondisi internal tiap negara,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:31.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia menemukan bukti suap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata benar.\NAku sudah menyiapkan pasukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:33.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyuap anggota dewan negara lain itu\Nmasalah internasional\NAku sudah menyiapkan pasukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisanya hanyalah tekad kalian.\NMenyuap anggota dewan negara lain itu\Nmasalah internasional
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan buktinya ada di perutku, kan?\NSisanya hanyalah tekad kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:39.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunjukkan cinta kalian pada negara,\Ndan buktinya ada di perutku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.\NTunjukkan cinta kalian pada negara,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:43.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}nyatakan tekad untuk memburu Raja Iblis,\NBerarti tinggal sodorkan saja dan selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maka aku akan menjatuhkan\Npalu penghakiman padanya!\NLapor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:46.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak diperlukan.\Nmaka aku akan menjatuhkan\Npalu penghakiman padanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:49.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa mengeluarkan bukti pun,\NMaster sudah menang.\NInilah saatnya umat manusia bangkit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:49.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa mengeluarkan bukti pun,\NMaster sudah menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:54.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marilah bersama-sama menjadi pahlawan\Nyang mengalahkan Raja Iblis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:58.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keputusan sudah keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:09:02.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena suara telah mencapai mayoritas,\Nagenda ini dinyatakan disetujui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:07.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benda ini mampu mengendalikan monster,\NPermata Pengendali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:13.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya benda itu sempat muncul waktu Milim\Npura-pura dikendalikan pas Walpurgis, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:20.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kelihatan asli, mustahil benda itu\Nbisa mengendalikanmu, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raja Iblis Rimuru,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:26.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau mau mengenakan permata ini,\Nakan kuperlakukan dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:29.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah menerima kenyataan\Ntanpa memberontak
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:32.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}merupakan cerminan martabat seorang raja?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:36.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kembalikan\Nkata-kata itu padamu, Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:39.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kamu sendiri\Nyang harus menerima kenyataan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:41.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:49.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya bukan begini!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rencana mereka menang lewat suap\Ndan gangguan spiritual gagal total.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:10:00.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang para anggota dewan itu sadar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}betapa bodohnya perbuatan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:06.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian mengkhianatiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar kata Tuan Elric!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:12.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi yang mengingkari janji,\Nkami akan setop bantua...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:15.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudnya itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:19.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu, maksudnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:23.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Proyek penanggulangan banjir\Ndi Kerajaan Rahbah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:26.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bantuan pangan untuk Kerajaan Carnada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:30.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu telah menjanjikan berbagai macam\Ndukungan kepada mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:32.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}He-Hei, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:37.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, kalau bantuan itu dihentikan\Nkarena tidak menuruti perintah,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:40.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukankah itu praktik suap yang cukup keji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:42.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu bisa tahu hal itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini hasil penyelidikan bawahanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:47.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sempat meragukan kebenarannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:51.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rupanya pelaku yang mengakuinya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:52.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada suap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sulit dipercaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bercanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:02.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Elric, kita tidak perlu menyerah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:06.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku bisa mengalahkan Raja Iblis,\Nmasalahnya bisa langsung selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:08.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, Reiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:13.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, kami masih punya kartu andalan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:19.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Elric, kami hanya berkewajiban\Nuntuk menjadi pengawal Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:22.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengecut hanya akan menghalangi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:26.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, Vert tidak ada hubungannya\Ndengan kasus ini, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:29.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya mereka punya\Ntujuan masing-masing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:33.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian masih mau melanjutkan\Ntindakan bodoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:38.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka mau mengambil tindakan ekstrem, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:41.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa saja meladeninya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lapor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:47.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Anda turun tangan sendiri,\Nreputasi Anda akan menurun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:52.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rimuru, biar aku yang mengurus orang ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu yakin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:57.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai saksi, aku tidak bisa\Nmembiarkan tindakan kurang ajar ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:02.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia sudah menghinaku habis-habisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:05.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Konyol sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:12.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau mau menjadi wanitaku sekarang,\Naku akan memanjakanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:16.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waduh, matilah dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:20.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Reiner, bukankah itu terlalu vulgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:23.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku juga tertarik dengan Raja Iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:26.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak sabar ingin menundukkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:30.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Idih, jangan bilang om-om itu\Nnaksir sama aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:31.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jijik.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:36.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal sudah kuperingatkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:39.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tidak menyangka kamu sebodoh ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:44.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kamu jadi congkak\Nkarena diperlakukan sebagai orang suci.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:50.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai yang terkuat di Kerajaan Ingrassia,\Nakan kubongkar sosok aslimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:53.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau aku\Nyang menghadapi Raja Iblis?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sampai dibunuh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:13:01.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tergantung dia bisa menahan tebasan\Npedang suci ini atau tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:06.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dia mau bertarung melawanku,\Nharusnya taklukkan dungeon dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuserahkan pada Benimaru saja, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.23,0:13:10.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Benima...\N- Dari tadi saya sudah menahan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:15.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian sudah terlewat lancang\Nterhadap Tuan Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:16.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:22.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar-benar meremehkanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:23.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raja Iblis Rimuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:28.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kamu tidak malu bersembunyi\Ndi belakang gadis yang lemah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, bukan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tutup mulutmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:35.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Rimuru dan Kakanda tidak perlu\Nsampai turun tangan melawanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:40.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski melawan wanita atau anak-anak,\Naku tidak akan berbelas kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:42.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Rimuru, biar saya\Nyang mengatasi kalau darurat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:45.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tenang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:49.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shuna terlihat baru selesai\Nmenganalisis orang itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:03.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertarungan di sana terlihat seru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:06.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:10.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena akan selesai dalam sekejap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:27.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat berdiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:31.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya yang terkuat di Kerajaan Ingrassia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:38.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ka-Kamu kenapa, kesatriaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:41.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya Orang Suci Hinata\Nbukanlah tandinganmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:46.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil!\NTidak mungkin aku bisa mengalahkannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasakan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya-Yang benar saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:06.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang bilang itu pedang suci,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:08.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ternyata sampah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:14.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beraninya monster sepertimu merendahkanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:21.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, ternyata Shuna bisa ilmu bela diri juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:24.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, dia mempelajari jujitsu dari Hakurou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:28.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:41.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupersembahkan doa ini untuk-Mu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:45.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikanlah kekuatan suci kepada hamba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:47.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}He-Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:50.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang rapalan itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengarkan dan kabulkanlah\Npermohonanku ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:57.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu! Sihir ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:16:00.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enyahkan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peleburan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:20.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, apa dia kebablasan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:27.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, masih hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:34.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, sebaiknya saya tidak menggunakan\Nsihir yang belum dikuasai dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:38.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rupanya gagal aktif\Nkarena ketidakmampuan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:42.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal dia sudah sangat menguasainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:45.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mu-Mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eng...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:50.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu Pangeran Elric, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih mau lanjut?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:57.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, bagaimana aku harus mengakhirinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:01.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lapor, ada hawa membunuh dari jarak jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Targetnya individu bernama Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:10.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:15.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senjata api?\NMana bisa sampai dari sejauh itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:21.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lapor, ini sejenis Pergerakan Spasial.\NKoneksi Spasial.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beelzebub!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:31.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran Elric!\NAnda baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:34.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beliau tidak terluka. Hebat sekali bisa\Nmenghentikannya dalam sekejap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:37.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:39.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:48.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benda sekecil ini bisa membunuh orang?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:52.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu peluru.\NButuh alat untuk menembakkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:55.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kenapa menargetkan Pangeran Elric?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:58.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin karena ingin menjatuhkan\Nreputasi Raja Iblis Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:03.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Pangeran Elric terbunuh dalam situasi itu,\Ndialah yang akan dicurigai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:11.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka hanya dimanfaatkan sebagai pion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:14.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa selama ini nyawaku terancam?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:17.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa akan baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rencana seseorang sudah berhasil digagalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:24.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ta-Tapi, aku masih bisa dimanfaatkan\Nsebagai calon raja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:27.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerajaan Ingrassia tidak selemah itu\Nsampai membiarkan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:30.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pangeran bodoh naik takhta, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:36.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjadi raja bukan satu-satunya\Npilihan hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:42.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin kamu bisa mencari makna hidup baru\Nsetelah menebus kejadian kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:48.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pikir Raja Iblis itu menakutkan\Ndan memusuhi manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:52.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya cinta damai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:58.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodohnya aku yang mudah tertipu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:01.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gaban, kita harus bertanggung jawab.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:08.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang Anda bicarakan?\NSaya tidak tahu apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:11.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya kamu yang mengusulkan rencana itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:15.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang ada buktinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:19.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Susah juga.\NHarus cari cara buat dia buka mulut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:23.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raja Aegil telah tiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:26.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hadirin, harap tenang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:30.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Ayahanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kedatangan sang Raja, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:47.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raja Iblis Tempest,\Nrupanya putraku telah berbuat onar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:51.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah, tapi kelihatannya dia sudah sadar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:58.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai ayahnya, aku minta maaf\Ndan kuucapkan terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:20:02.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumaafkan, tapi tidak akan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:04.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingat baik-baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:09.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pun berharap\Nkita dapat menjalin hubungan yang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon kerja samanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:12.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:18.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:23.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cukup, kamu harus dididik ulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:26.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:28.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gaban.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:31.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang ingin aku tanyakan padamu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:34.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sepertinya kamu tidak mau cerita.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:38.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sa-Saya tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:44.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menyerahkanmu pada Inkuisitor Sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:48.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Ampuni saya!\NSaya akan bicara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:52.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya minta belas kasih Anda!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:55.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini juga rencananya Maribel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:59.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mengerti lagi.\NApa yang dia pikirkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:02.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasihani saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:09.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah, para dalang kerusuhan itu\Nakhirnya digiring keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:15.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah itu, sidang dilanjutkan\Ndan tiga poin utama resmi diterima.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:20.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, mengakui Tempest\Nsebagai sebuah negara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:24.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kedua, meresmikan keanggotaan Tempest\Ndalam Dewan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:29.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketiga, menyerahkan otoritas militer\NDewan kepada Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:32.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua poin tersebut telah disahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:37.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pun menyadari sesuatu\Nsetelah kejadian ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:40.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Adu licik dengan para anggota dewan\Nbukanlah gayaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:45.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali kuserahkan pada Kak Raphael saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.34,0:21:55.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil, kenapa hawa keberadaan\NElric masih ada?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:57.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu tembakan lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:03.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, ini karena aku meremehkan\Nmajikan para monster itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.47,0:22:04.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:11.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu meremehkan Tuan Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:18.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Betapa bodohnya masih diam di tempat\Nsetelah gagal membunuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:58.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, "Identitas sang Dalang".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:24:00.04,tanda-5,Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(975,0)\c&H0F1560&\3c&HC6E0E4&}Identitas sang{\bord0} {\u1\c&HC6E0E4&}Dalang
